//! GPU texture atlas packers.
//!
//! This module is the Phase-3 placement companion to the [`crate::material_pbr`]
//! policy substrate. The packer at [`gpu_atlas::GreedyAtlas`] is a pure-Rust,
//! `std`-only 2D shelf-bin packer that the Bevy adapter feeds to the GPU at
//! startup to build the resolution-free material atlas.
//!
//! The module intentionally has no dependency on `bevy`, `wgpu`, or any
//! asset loader — it only deals with bytes and rectangles. The Bevy
//! adapter translates the returned `placements: HashMap<String, Rect>` into
//! `wgpu::TextureCopyTextureInfo` source rects at upload time.
//!
//! ## Layout
//!
//! - [`gpu_atlas`] — the packer itself, plus its `Rect` and `AtlasTexture`
//!   return types. Unit tests for 1, 5, 50 texture cases live in the same
//!   file under `#[cfg(test)] mod tests`.

pub mod gpu_atlas;

pub use gpu_atlas::{
    AtlasTexture, GreedyAtlas, GreedyAtlasConfig, PackError, PackResult, Rect,
};